oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hollywood Rodeo - Audition - Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part 2 of an audition recording of Hollywood Rodeo, starring Tex Ritter. Also featuring the Rancho Trio, Soapy Jones (played by Roscoe Ates), Bob McJimpsey, and guest Yakima Canutt.
